response.overview: The need for an informative and candid safer sex guide for lesbians is clear. In "Well Sexy Women" you will see frank presentations of the practicalities and sensuality of safer sex in today's threatening world. Made by and for lesbians with stunning beauty and openness, "Well Sexy Women" doesn't shy away from sensitive subjects, delivering timely information in a sensual and passionate way. Six beautiful women explicitly demonstrate safer sex techniques erotically. The facts without the sermon.
response.tagline: A Lesbian's Guide To Safer Sex
response.title: Well Sexy Women
